{"type": "article", "id": 10242, "title": "“残缺”的容器", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-01T07:41:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523535783CpMlXaWISYN4H9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t法国设计师 Marie Liebhardt 推出了一套容器作品，命名为“残缺”，一套为金属材质，一套为瓷器材质，其共同点在于在产品的表面通过纹理的设计和制作，营造出“残缺”的效果。其设计灵感来自于城市中墙壁和街道等随着时间的流逝老化后的模样，用作品来表现时间的流逝和光阴的印记。这是<a href=\"http://marieliebhardt.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353542TBzEJNblZhprtcn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235355PMrXh4WuKfZyt9Jl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235355lIu50rkHADp23RwW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235355BvsprjNE9O4mRKPn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235356CHdEXRm0w9QkJKSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235356akPZzi0HAU72gbQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}